# LapViewer Base Agent

Read `docs/agents/BASE_AGENT.md` for the doc map, process tiers, and guardrails.

**Derive live state — don't assume it.** Run `git remote -v` and `git status -sb`, or read `docs/agents/PROJECT_STATE.generated.md` (regenerated each session).

**Procedures — invoke skills:**
| Skill | Use when |
|-------|----------|
| `lapviewer-feature` | New feature: idea → spec → ready work order |
| `lapviewer-pickup` | Process Ready work items (typed agents) |
| `lapviewer-promote` | Merge to `dev`, promote to `master`, push |

**Guardrails:** Do not implement `Draft` work without approval. Ask before dependencies, data deletion, deploy, or adding a git remote. Git per D-012; never change `git config`, force-push `dev`/`master`, or commit secrets.

Branch conventions: `.cursor/rules/lapviewer-git-workflow.mdc`.
